name: 10 Memory Card - Guererro
description: You must have heard this name from a TV program from the 2000s. Right! Eddie Guerrero is the name of a WWF wrestler. But this axolotl Guerrero is a tattoo artist as well as a skateboarder who has the life principle of "It takes a revolution, to create a solution". Although his face looks unfriendly, he has a soft heart.
